title: Trina and Brittney Taylor interview and more
itunes:title: Trina and Brittney Taylor interview and more
description:
Today on the show we had Trina and Brittney Taylor in the building where they spoke about Love and Hip Hop, sex toys, and Trina definitely did not hide her shady comments when it came to responding back to Khia. Moreover, we flashed back to when Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Shad Moss and we also flashed back to some listeners asking Angela Yee and Charlamagne and Envy ( C&E ) during "Ask Yee."
